reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Good value for price. Easy to assemble. Look nice and decent quality- perfect size

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Perfect! I like the slightly smaller tray surface vs. the ones my daughter has as they aren’t so overpowering. The black is classy and these are a great buy.Don’t know why some reviews said unstable as these are sturdy and I feel secure in putting drinks on them.Note that they are not high enough to go over the arm of the sofa but I didn’t want them for that purpose. Just measure your sofa and the description on Amazon shows a picture with all measurements. No one should be surprised.So EASY to put together and I’m a 75 year-old grandma. Each piece is clearly marked (the stickers come off easy if removed slowly) and hardware is separately bagged. There’s even a bag of “spares”! Directions have pictures and clear instructions. Bravo!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Small but Attractive
reviews.reviewText: Very attractive tables. They were shorter than we anticipated, which is our fault for not reading the sizing description clearly. Look closely at that so you know if it'll work for you or not. They're too short to use comfortably as a tray table for comfortably eating a meal while sitting on the couch. They're too short to go over the arm rest of our couch, too. But we ended up using them as small side tables for a rocking chair and will use them for guests when they come over so they have somewhere to set their drink or phone, or whatever and they're great for that. Very nice colors. Seem to be good and sturdy, don't wobble too easily even when our boisterous dog is running around playing with toys and bumps into them. Way sturdier than the fold-able tray tables, that's for sure. Would make a great item for small spaces or corners when you need a surface but don't have a ton of room. Assembled quickly and easily. Highly recommended, just make sure you look closely at sizing so it'll fit what you need it to do.
